{"tid":2161970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油麻地男子公園睡一睡　數百元連揹袋被偷嘆無奈","createTime":"2020-08-18T01:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T02:37:46.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"24523719c8bc769333ac473169d1e88c6bfb110a","tid":2161970,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6oTpRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6oTpRY.jpg&h=db6d3136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男事主向警員講述案發經過。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<br />\n今日(18)清晨6時許，一名年約60歲男子於油麻地寧波街近上海街一休憩公園報案，指他於上址小休期間疑倦極睡着；詎料一覺醒來時，發現懷中的揹袋不翼而飛，相信被人趁機偷去，袋中裝有現金數百元。警員將案件列盜竊跟進，正設法追查涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200818/mobile/bkn-20200818062914273-0818_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200818%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200818062914273-0818_00822_001.html&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21IoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=41ddb9ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200818/mobile/bkn-20200818062914273-0818_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4ecdf2c3ae71b1e5b4c93dd7b8109f70898c6350","tid":2161970,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:09:36.000Z","msg":"幾百蚊小事啦<br />\n你而家公眾戶外地方冇戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05501f93ac84f8e81f39e139b5bd34d5c42086e","tid":2161970,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />渣ga"},{"pid":"efa4a9ff1df96e2e899c47253277460b35d8cbe4","tid":2161970,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05f53fa7881944cf07da9459ed820261c9275606","tid":2161970,"uid":256783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:16:43.000Z","msg":"睇樣似藍屍 <br />\n<br />\n藍屍偷藍屍 然